This file consolidates required attributions for third-party
inspiration, design, or code referenced inside the Sunfish codebase.
Direct npm / NuGet / cargo dependencies are attributed through their
respective package metadata and ship under their original LICENSE
files; this NOTICE covers "borrow with attribution" relationships
where Sunfish code structure follows the shape of an upstream
open-source project without vendoring the project's source.

License-posture policy: ADR 0088 §3 (Anchor) + ADR 0088 §2 (clean-
room vs borrow-with-attribution distinction).


